Text: Nice story to finish like that. Liked your playlists very much, simply the best on the net. Kind of replaced my radio lately. will miss you. Will try to seed your collection as long as possible. Thanks for everything.

Thx One. I know the lists are good (listened most music on the net). However, I hope not too good :) The idea is to inspire people to buy their music. Its not commercial but its like the sixties. New and worth listening. And now there is internet. Thanks for the support.
